      • parse

        public static Hypergraph parse(java.util.Scanner scanner)
        Creates a hypergraph from a stream of characters. The character string should be formatted like this: 
         # Empty lines and lines that start with '#' are ignored
 # The remaining lines should contain a comma-separated list of
 # vertex numbers (integers)
 0,1,2,3
 1,2,4
 2,3,6,1
 ...
        Parameters:
        s - The string, formatted as specified above
        Returns:
        A hypergraph, or null if the graph could not be created
